				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Jaheira's granddaughter that is inside - she's earnest and friendly.\r\n\r\nHer clue that she supplies the player with is to do with how to access Jaheira's hidden items in the basement - that puzzle is 4 orbs you hit with different spells to produce little platforms and jump across to get to her personal gear."
